sentences: Nitesh Pradhan (born 11 May 1990) known professionally as Nitesh R Pradhan is an Indian journalist based in Sikkim, India.
Nitesh Pradhan (born 11 May 1990) known professionally as Nitesh R Pradhan is an Indian journalist based in Sikkim, India.
He is the editor of The Voice of Sikkim online web portal and the founder of independent online news portal Eastern Himalayan News Service.
He is also a singer-lyricist as part of pop duo Anisha & Nitesh.

He started singing in the pop duo Anisha & Nitesh since it was formed in 2013 – it was the first pop duo (mixed) act from Sikkim – and has released many Nepali language songs including the chartbuster Maya.

His work in media includes print and digital media houses notably  TNT- The Northeast Today, Sikkim Chronicle, Summit Times, Assam Tribune & East Mojo.
He reports on a range of such topics as environment, geopolitics, gender, LGBTQ, society and culture of the  Eastern Himalayan region.
In 2020, he founded independent online news portal Eastern Himalayan News Service.
